OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be
OL,6,Frather cloudy with outbreaks of rain,
OL,7,Fthis heavy in the south. The best of
OL,8,Fany drier spells will be in the
OL,9,Fnortheast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FCloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,12,Fat first. This soon clears to bright
OL,13,Fspells with the odd afternoon shower.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMostly
OL,16,Fcloudy with showery rain at times.
OL,17,FOutbreaks of rain will become heavy
OL,18,Ffor a time Wednesday afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
